         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Dr. Inventory
Cr. GR/IR Account
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-12078B9E-F3F3-4D4C-BE10-5DB53A69EFA7" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Based on Inventory Update Program Stock type change may happen from Unrestricted and Blocked also. (Refers MQCS data and moves the stock)
</text>
